+--------------------------------------------------------+
| GXTracking/backport is executing the same task as      +
| GXTracking but using the Geant4 library                +
+--------------------------------------------------------+

1. CMake is set up for the whole compilation.

2. Apply the patch geant4.simplification.diff (originally made againt geant4 v4.9.5) and rebuild Geant4.

3. How to build

   mkdir bin ; cd bin
   cmake -DGeant4_DIR=<full_path_geant4_installation> PROJECT=tracking ..
   make

4. How to run

   4.1 prepare data (EM tables, Magnetic field map)

   ln -s <path_to_g4hpcbenchmark>/GPTracking/data data   
   ln -s <path_to_g4hpcbenchmark>/GPTransportation/cmsExp.mag.3_8T \
         cmsExp.mag.3_8T 

   3.2 run test programs: example

   ./tracking <run_option>

   where <run option>: 1 - one kernel 
                       2 - electron/photon kernels

